skins.shipDescription: J-class destroyer C Jupiter, Hull Number F85.
skins.selfIntroduction: I am the J class destroyer with improved torpedo equipment, Jupiter... "Juno"? We're just sisters. I-60? I think I sank her, but...
skins.acquisition: I am the Royal Navy J-class destroyer, Jupiter... "Jue-know"? Erm, which one are you referring to?
skins.login: Ju-Juno, you don't need to be concerned about me... I've been in this longer than you...
skins.secretaryIdle2: It's fun to be with you, Commander...
skins.secretaryIdle3: I hope I'll... get to come home some day...
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander... my hands... are they warm...?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Huh...?! It wasn't Juno, but you, Commander?!

skins.shipDescription: Good evening, Commander. There's a new show on the telly. You want to watch with me?
skins.acquisition: Good evening, Commander. There's a new show on the telly. You want to watch with me?
skins.login: That new show is about to start. Hehe. I've been looking forward to it. Are you interested, Commander?
skins.details: Huh? Where's my slipper...? Oh, it's behind me? Thanks, Commander...
skins.secretaryIdle1: My torpedo pillow...? Hugging it... makes me feel very safe...
skins.secretaryIdle2: I do wish Juno was here. But having you with me, Commander, that makes me very happy too. Hehe~
skins.secretaryIdle3: I heard a rumor that a certain Ghost of the Eagle Union and a Demon from the Sakura Empire are interested in this show too.
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander, can you please not tell my sisters... how I spend all night watching TV?
